<h2 style="margin-top:0;">Follow-Up Reminder</h2>
<p>Hi {{agentName}},</p>
<p>You have <strong>{{leads.length}}</strong> lead(s) scheduled for follow-up today.</p>

<table class="details">
  <tr>
    <td style="font-weight:600;background-color:#f9fafb;">Client</td>
    <td style="font-weight:600;background-color:#f9fafb;">Priority</td>
  </tr>
  {{#each leads}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{this.clientName}}</td>
    <td>{{this.priority}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
</table>

<div class="info-box">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> Consistent follow-ups are key to converting leads. Make sure to log your activity after each interaction.
</div>
